68
00:04:01,833 --> 00:04:04,416
[KIYOSHI] I will, Chiyo.
What an awesome girl!

69
00:04:04,500 --> 00:04:06,708
Dammit, I don't wanna
split up with her!

70
00:04:06,791 --> 00:04:08,541
