oppressive hell-hole!

93
00:04:49,791 --> 00:04:51,500
[groans]

94
00:04:51,583 --> 00:04:53,625
[KIYOSHI] Great plan,
Gakuto. Incredible.

95
00:04:53,708 --> 00:04:55,166
[SHINGO]
Just brilliant.

96
00:04:59,791 --> 00:05:01,583
