[CHIYO]
Huh?

104
00:05:19,708 --> 00:05:21,750
[MEIKO] Each requested item
cooked to perfection.

105
00:05:21,833 --> 00:05:23,000
Enjoy your last meal.

106
00:05:23,083 --> 00:05:24,291
[SHINGO]
Damn, that smells good!

107
00:05:24,375 --> 00:05:26,166
[hollers] I, myself,
have chosen the most

108
