grasshopper-sized saddles.

136
00:06:19,750 --> 00:06:21,375
[GAKUTO] There's no time
for ludicrous musings.

137
00:06:21,458 --> 00:06:22,916
Now hurry up
and finish your meals!

138
00:06:23,000 --> 00:06:25,708
[retching]

139
00:06:25,791 --> 00:06:28,291
