meal have they given me?

140
00:06:28,375 --> 00:06:30,375
[JOE] Fried grasshoppers
over rice, dude?

141
00:06:30,458 --> 00:06:32,625
Indeed! But why
serve them to me?

142
00:06:32,708 --> 00:06:34,750
