Please excuse me.

168
00:07:29,000 --> 00:07:30,125
[door squeaks, thuds]

169
00:07:30,208 --> 00:07:32,375
[CHAIRMAN] Hmmm.
[door squeaks, thuds]

170
00:07:32,458 --> 00:07:35,416
[gasps]

171
