in some blinds soon!

172
00:07:38,666 --> 00:07:40,541
[GAKUTO] And that's
my plan in a nutshell.

173
00:07:40,625 --> 00:07:43,416
Come tomorrow, we shall
set it in motion, my brothers.

174
00:07:43,500 --> 00:07:44,791
[chuckles]

175
00:07:44,875 --> 00:07:46,458
It would seem my plan's
brilliance is so astounding,

176
00:07:46,541 --> 00:07:48,125
