the lot of you speechless!

177
00:07:48,208 --> 00:07:50,000
Well, I wouldn't go that far.

178
00:07:50,083 --> 00:07:51,333
[GAKUTO]
Hm?

179
00:07:51,416 --> 00:07:52,666
