190
00:08:08,958 --> 00:08:10,958
If we are indeed
to be expelled tomorrow,

191
00:08:11,041 --> 00:08:12,666
then this plan hasn't a chance.

192
00:08:12,750 --> 00:08:14,833
Well. I hope you
enjoyed your meals.

193
00:08:14,916 --> 00:08:17,666
There's some paper work you
germ-farms need to fill out.

194
00:08:17,750 --> 00:08:18,958
Your withdrawal requests.

195
00:08:19,041 --> 00:08:20,166
[BOYS gasp]

196
00:08:20,250 --> 00:08:22,208
It's funny. I doubt that
school life will be

197
00:08:22,291 --> 00:08:25,458
quite as lively once the five
of you are out of here.

198
00:08:25,541 --> 00:08:27,458
[KIYOSHI] Is it just me,
or does it almost sound like

199
00:08:27,541 --> 00:08:29,791
